<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="散る散る満ちる"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="鷲尾伶菜"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Just Wanna Sing"/><amll:meta key="album" value="散る散る満ちる"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPU902104883"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1907015019"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1933301818"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="5N8xU3TeSLHgS0Xxb4a8zA"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:08.690"><div begin="22.890" end="4:08.690"><p begin="22.890" end="31.600" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="22.890" end="23.660">昔</span> <span begin="24.100" end="24.750">誰</span><span begin="25.260" end="25.570">か</span><span begin="25.570" end="25.890">が</span><span begin="26.040" end="26.230">言</span><span begin="26.230" end="26.340">っ</span><span begin="26.340" end="26.480">て</span><span begin="26.480" end="26.770">た</span> <span begin="27.700" end="27.970">満</span><span begin="27.970" end="28.280">月</span><span begin="28.280" end="28.430">の</span><span begin="28.430" end="28.860">光</span><span begin="28.860" end="29.040">は</span><span begin="29.040" end="29.490">人</span><span begin="29.490" end="29.630">の</span><span begin="29.630" end="30.050">心</span><span begin="30.050" end="30.300">を</span><span begin="30.300" end="30.660">狂</span><span begin="30.660" end="30.940">わ</span><span begin="30.940" end="31.270">せ</span><span begin="31.270" end="31.600">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">很久以前有人曾说 满月的光芒会让人心发狂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">很久以前有人曾說 滿月的光芒會讓人心發狂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Long ago someone said the light of the full moon drives people&apos;s hearts mad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">예전 누군가가 말했지 만월의 빛은 사람의 마음을 미치게 한다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Autrefois quelqu&apos;un a dit que la lumière de la pleine lune rendait les cœurs fous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hace tiempo alguien dijo que la luz de la luna llena enloquece el corazón de las personas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Früher hat mal jemand gesagt das Licht des Vollmonds treibt die Herzen der Menschen in den Wahnsinn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Alguém disse uma vez que a luz da lua cheia enlouquece o coração das pessoas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давным-давно кто-то сказал что свет полной луны сводит людей с ума</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tempo fa qualcuno diceva la luce della luna piena fa impazzire il cuore delle persone</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mukashi dareka ga itteta mangetsu no hikari wa hito no kokoro o kuruwaseru</span></p><p begin="32.480" end="40.360" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.480" end="33.220">昔</span> <span begin="33.670" end="34.400">誰</span><span begin="34.870" end="35.180">か</span><span begin="35.180" end="35.510">が</span><span begin="35.620" end="35.830">言</span><span begin="35.830" end="35.940">っ</span><span begin="35.940" end="36.080">て</span><span begin="36.080" end="36.330">た</span> <span begin="36.670" end="37.120">桜</span><span begin="37.120" end="37.270">の</span><span begin="37.270" end="37.410">木</span><span begin="37.410" end="37.560">は</span><span begin="37.560" end="37.850">脆</span><span begin="37.850" end="38.020">い</span> <span begin="38.020" end="38.320">傷</span><span begin="38.320" end="38.480">を</span><span begin="38.480" end="38.610">つ</span><span begin="38.610" end="38.760">け</span><span begin="38.760" end="38.930">る</span><span begin="38.930" end="39.070">と</span><span begin="39.070" end="39.210">枯</span><span begin="39.210" end="39.370">れ</span><span begin="39.370" end="39.520">て</span><span begin="39.630" end="40.000">し</span><span begin="40.000" end="40.240">ま</span><span begin="40.240" end="40.360">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">很久以前有人曾说 樱花树很脆弱 只要受伤就会枯萎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">很久以前有人曾說 櫻花樹很脆弱 只要受傷就會枯萎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Long ago someone said cherry trees are fragile if you scratch them they will wither</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">예전 누군가가 말했지 벚나무는 연약해서 상처를 입히면 시들어 버린다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Autrefois quelqu&apos;un a dit que les cerisiers sont fragiles qu&apos;ils se flétrissent si on les blesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hace tiempo alguien dijo que los cerezos son frágiles y si los hieres se marchitan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Früher hat mal jemand gesagt Kirschbäume sind zerbrechlich wenn man sie verletzt verdorren sie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Alguém disse uma vez que a cerejeira é frágil se a machucar ela murchará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давным-давно кто-то сказал что сакура хрупка если её ранить она засохнет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tempo fa qualcuno diceva i ciliegi sono fragili se li ferisci appassiscono</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mukashi dareka ga itteta sakura no ki wa moroi kizu o tsukeru to karete shimau</span></p><p begin="40.570" end="44.770" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.570" end="40.900">ど</span><span begin="40.900" end="41.200">う</span><span begin="41.200" end="42.090">に</span><span begin="42.090" end="42.380">も</span><span begin="42.380" end="42.580">で</span><span begin="42.690" end="43.000">き</span><span begin="43.000" end="43.600">な</span><span begin="43.600" end="44.770">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无能为力</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無能為力</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t do anything about it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌할 방도가 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je n&apos;y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No puedo hacer nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kann nichts tun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não há nada que eu possa fazer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ничего не поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ci posso fare niente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dounimo dekinai</span></p><p begin="45.360" end="49.990" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.360" end="46.010">恋</span><span begin="46.010" end="46.600">の</span><span begin="46.600" end="47.180">結</span><span begin="47.180" end="47.500">び</span><span begin="47.500" end="47.760">目</span><span begin="47.760" end="47.960">が</span><span begin="48.070" end="48.360">ほ</span><span begin="48.360" end="48.890">ど</span><span begin="48.990" end="49.580">け</span><span begin="49.580" end="49.990">ず</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">解不开这爱恋的死结</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">解不開這愛戀的死結</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The knot of love won&apos;t come undone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑의 매듭이 풀리지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le nœud de l&apos;amour ne se défait pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El nudo del amor no se desata</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Knoten der Liebe löst sich nicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O nó do amor não se desfaz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Узел любви не развязывается</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il nodo dell&apos;amore non si scioglie</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koi no musubime ga hodokezu</span></p><p begin="50.140" end="54.420" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.140" end="50.470">ど</span><span begin="50.470" end="50.780">う</span><span begin="50.780" end="51.680">に</span><span begin="51.680" end="51.980">も</span><span begin="51.980" end="52.180">で</span><span begin="52.280" end="52.600">き</span><span begin="52.600" end="53.190">な</span><span begin="53.190" end="54.420">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无可奈何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無可奈何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t do anything about it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌할 방도가 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je n&apos;y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No puedo hacer nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kann nichts tun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não há nada que eu possa fazer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ничего не поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ci posso fare niente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dounimo dekinai</span></p><p begin="54.910" end="1:00.480" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.910" end="55.290">逢</span><span begin="55.290" end="55.570">い</span><span begin="55.570" end="56.180">た</span><span begin="56.460" end="56.710">く</span><span begin="56.810" end="57.230">て</span><span begin="57.430" end="57.700">ま</span><span begin="57.700" end="57.990">た</span><span begin="57.990" end="58.290">痛</span><span begin="58.290" end="58.420">い</span><span begin="58.420" end="58.820">痛</span><span begin="58.820" end="58.930">い</span><span begin="58.930" end="1:00.360">痛</span><span begin="1:00.360" end="1:00.480">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想见你又心痛心痛心痛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想見你又心痛心痛心痛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to see you so it hurts hurts hurts again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">만나고 싶어서 또 아파 아파 아파</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux te voir et ça fait encore mal mal mal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero verte y me duele duele duele otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will dich sehen und es tut wieder weh weh weh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero te ver e de novo dói dói dói</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хочу встретиться и снова больно больно больно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio vederti e fa ancora male male male</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aitakute mata itai itai itai</span></p><p begin="1:00.980" end="1:05.410" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.980" end="1:01.460">満</span><span begin="1:01.460" end="1:02.200">月</span><span begin="1:02.200" end="1:02.420">の</span><span begin="1:02.420" end="1:03.080">下</span><span begin="1:03.080" end="1:03.330">で</span> <span begin="1:03.330" end="1:04.250">桜</span><span begin="1:04.250" end="1:04.460">散</span><span begin="1:04.460" end="1:04.850">る</span><span begin="1:04.850" end="1:05.030">散</span><span begin="1:05.030" end="1:05.410">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">满月之下 樱花飘落散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">滿月之下 櫻花飄落散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Under the full moon cherry blossoms scatter scatter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">만월 아래서 벚꽃이 지고 져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sous la pleine lune les fleurs de cerisier tombent tombent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Bajo la luna llena los cerezos caen y caen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unter dem Vollmond fallen fallen die Kirschblüten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sob a lua cheia as cerejeiras caem caem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Под полной луной сакура опадает опадает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sotto la luna piena i ciliegi cadono cadono</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mangetsu no shita de sakura chiru chiru</span></p><p begin="1:05.720" end="1:10.280" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.720" end="1:06.260">情</span><span begin="1:06.370" end="1:07.580">熱</span><span begin="1:07.580" end="1:07.900">は</span><span begin="1:07.900" end="1:08.080">満</span><span begin="1:08.180" end="1:08.780">ち</span><span begin="1:08.780" end="1:10.280">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">热情满溢充盈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">熱情滿溢充盈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Passion fills up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정열은 차올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La passion déborde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La pasión se desborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Leidenschaft erfüllt mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A paixão transborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Страсть переполняет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La passione si colma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jounetsu wa michiru</span></p><p begin="1:11.120" end="1:19.890" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.120" end="1:11.630">そ</span><span begin="1:11.800" end="1:12.090">の</span><span begin="1:12.090" end="1:12.650">優</span><span begin="1:12.650" end="1:12.940">し</span><span begin="1:12.940" end="1:13.280">さ</span><span begin="1:13.280" end="1:13.570">は</span><span begin="1:13.570" end="1:14.750">私</span><span begin="1:14.750" end="1:15.340">を</span><span begin="1:16.250" end="1:16.520">悲</span><span begin="1:16.520" end="1:16.740">し</span><span begin="1:16.850" end="1:17.120">く</span><span begin="1:17.120" end="1:17.440">さ</span><span begin="1:17.440" end="1:17.780">せ</span><span begin="1:17.780" end="1:18.040">る</span><span begin="1:18.040" end="1:18.350">だ</span><span begin="1:18.350" end="1:19.240">け</span><span begin="1:19.240" end="1:19.530">で</span><span begin="1:19.530" end="1:19.890">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那份温柔只会让我感到悲伤</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那份溫柔只會讓我感到悲傷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That kindness only makes me sad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 다정함은 나를 슬프게 할 뿐입니다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette gentillesse ne fait que m&apos;attrister</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa amabilidad solo me entristece</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diese Freundlichkeit macht mich nur traurig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Essa sua gentileza apenas me deixa triste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эта доброта лишь заставляет меня грустить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quella gentilezza mi rende solo triste</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono yasashisa wa watashi o kanashiku saseru dake desu</span></p><p begin="1:20.180" end="1:22.830" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:20.180" end="1:20.560">ま</span><span begin="1:20.560" end="1:20.630">っ</span><span begin="1:20.630" end="1:21.080">さ</span><span begin="1:21.080" end="1:21.370">ら</span><span begin="1:21.370" end="1:21.650">に</span><span begin="1:21.650" end="1:21.870">な</span><span begin="1:21.870" end="1:22.280">り</span><span begin="1:22.280" end="1:22.580">た</span><span begin="1:22.580" end="1:22.830">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想回到最初的纯白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想回到最初的純白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to become brand new</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">백지가 되고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux redevenir immaculée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero empezar de cero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte ganz rein werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero voltar a ser uma página em branco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хочу стать совершенно новой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio tornare immacolata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Massara ni naritai</span></p><p begin="1:22.830" end="1:29.240" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:22.830" end="1:23.070">あ</span><span begin="1:23.070" end="1:23.460">な</span><span begin="1:23.460" end="1:23.640">た</span><span begin="1:23.640" end="1:24.070">知</span><span begin="1:24.070" end="1:24.270">ら</span><span begin="1:24.270" end="1:24.550">な</span><span begin="1:24.550" end="1:24.630">い</span> <span begin="1:24.970" end="1:25.290">あ</span><span begin="1:25.290" end="1:25.520">の</span><span begin="1:25.520" end="1:26.110">日</span><span begin="1:26.480" end="1:26.790">の</span><span begin="1:26.790" end="1:28.000">私</span><span begin="1:28.000" end="1:29.240">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">还不认识你的 那天的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還不認識你的 那天的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The me from that day who didn&apos;t know you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신을 모르던 그날의 나는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Celle que j&apos;étais ce jour-là et que tu ne connais pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi yo de aquel día que no te conocía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein damaliges Ich das dich nicht kannte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A mim daquele dia que não te conhecia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Та я из того дня не знавшая тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La me di quel giorno che non ti conosceva</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata shiranai ano hi no watashi wa</span></p><p begin="1:29.730" end="1:39.370" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.730" end="1:30.400">月</span><span begin="1:30.400" end="1:30.880">の</span><span begin="1:31.270" end="1:32.770">光</span><span begin="1:32.770" end="1:33.260">に</span><span begin="1:33.710" end="1:34.270">瞞</span><span begin="1:34.270" end="1:34.520">か</span><span begin="1:34.520" end="1:34.860">さ</span><span begin="1:34.860" end="1:35.030">れ</span><span begin="1:35.170" end="1:35.660">て</span><span begin="1:36.050" end="1:36.390">し</span><span begin="1:36.390" end="1:36.970">ま</span><span begin="1:37.260" end="1:37.580">っ</span><span begin="1:37.580" end="1:39.370">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被那月光彻底蒙蔽了双眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被那月光徹底蒙蔽了雙眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Was completely deceived by the moonlight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">달빛에 속아 넘어가 버렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">A été trompée par la lumière de la lune</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Fui engañada por la luz de la luna</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wurde vom Mondlicht getäuscht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fui enganada pela luz da lua</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Была обманута лунным светом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È stata ingannata dalla luce della luna</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuki no hikari ni mayakasarete shimatta</span></p><p begin="1:43.240" end="1:52.000" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.240" end="1:44.030">昔</span> <span begin="1:44.490" end="1:45.170">誰</span><span begin="1:45.680" end="1:46.020">か</span><span begin="1:46.020" end="1:46.330">が</span><span begin="1:46.440" end="1:46.630">言</span><span begin="1:46.630" end="1:46.740">っ</span><span begin="1:46.740" end="1:46.880">て</span><span begin="1:46.880" end="1:47.160">た</span> <span begin="1:48.050" end="1:48.210">夜</span><span begin="1:48.210" end="1:48.510">中</span><span begin="1:48.510" end="1:48.640">に</span><span begin="1:48.640" end="1:48.970">爪</span><span begin="1:48.970" end="1:49.110">切</span><span begin="1:49.110" end="1:49.270">る</span><span begin="1:49.270" end="1:49.360">な</span><span begin="1:49.360" end="1:49.560">良</span><span begin="1:49.560" end="1:49.890">く</span><span begin="1:49.890" end="1:50.020">な</span><span begin="1:50.020" end="1:50.170">い</span><span begin="1:50.170" end="1:50.300">こ</span><span begin="1:50.300" end="1:50.470">と</span><span begin="1:50.470" end="1:50.590">が</span><span begin="1:50.590" end="1:50.660">起</span><span begin="1:50.760" end="1:51.070">こ</span><span begin="1:51.070" end="1:51.270">る</span><span begin="1:51.380" end="1:51.690">か</span><span begin="1:51.690" end="1:52.000">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">很久以前有人曾说 半夜别剪指甲会发生不好的事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">很久以前有人曾說 半夜別剪指甲會發生不好的事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Long ago someone said don&apos;t cut your nails at night because bad things will happen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">예전 누군가가 말했지 한밤중에 손톱 깎지 말라고 안 좋은 일이 일어날 테니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Autrefois quelqu&apos;un a dit de ne pas se couper les ongles la nuit car il arrivera malheur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hace tiempo alguien dijo no te cortes las uñas de noche porque pasarán cosas malas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Früher hat mal jemand gesagt schneide nachts nicht die Nägel weil dann etwas Schlechtes passiert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Alguém disse uma vez não corte as unhas à noite porque coisas ruins vão acontecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давным-давно кто-то сказал не стриги ногти ночью иначе случится беда</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tempo fa qualcuno diceva non tagliare le unghie di notte perché accadrà qualcosa di brutto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mukashi dareka ga itteta yonaka ni tsume kiru na yokunai koto ga okoru kara</span></p><p begin="1:52.870" end="2:00.700" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.870" end="1:53.600">昔</span> <span begin="1:54.090" end="1:54.740">誰</span><span begin="1:55.290" end="1:55.580">か</span><span begin="1:55.580" end="1:55.920">が</span><span begin="1:56.040" end="1:56.210">言</span><span begin="1:56.210" end="1:56.320">っ</span><span begin="1:56.320" end="1:56.460">て</span><span begin="1:56.460" end="1:56.720">た</span> <span begin="1:57.080" end="1:57.380">黒</span><span begin="1:57.380" end="1:57.670">猫</span><span begin="1:57.670" end="1:57.830">が</span><span begin="1:57.830" end="1:58.100">通</span><span begin="1:58.100" end="1:58.250">る</span><span begin="1:58.250" end="1:58.360">と</span><span begin="1:58.360" end="1:58.820">幸</span><span begin="1:58.820" end="1:58.970">せ</span><span begin="1:58.970" end="1:59.160">ひ</span><span begin="1:59.160" end="1:59.300">と</span><span begin="1:59.300" end="1:59.480">つ</span><span begin="1:59.480" end="1:59.630">逃</span><span begin="1:59.630" end="1:59.790">げ</span><span begin="1:59.790" end="1:59.950">て</span><span begin="2:00.060" end="2:00.410">し</span><span begin="2:00.410" end="2:00.620">ま</span><span begin="2:00.620" end="2:00.700">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">很久以前有人曾说 黑猫走过就会溜走一份幸福</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">很久以前有人曾說 黑貓走過就會溜走一份幸福</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Long ago someone said if a black cat passes by a piece of happiness will run away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">예전 누군가가 말했지 검은 고양이가 지나가면 행복이 하나 달아나 버린다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Autrefois quelqu&apos;un a dit que si un chat noir passe un bonheur s&apos;échappe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hace tiempo alguien dijo que si pasa un gato negro se escapa una felicidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Früher hat mal jemand gesagt wenn eine schwarze Katze vorbeigeht flieht ein Stück Glück</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Alguém disse uma vez que se um gato preto cruzar o caminho uma felicidade escapa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давным-давно кто-то сказал если пробежит чёрная кошка одно счастье ускользнёт</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tempo fa qualcuno diceva se passa un gatto nero una felicità scappa via</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mukashi dareka ga itteta kuroneko ga tooru to shiawase hitotsu nigete shimau</span></p><p begin="2:00.930" end="2:05.170" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.930" end="2:01.580">信</span><span begin="2:01.580" end="2:02.440">じ</span><span begin="2:02.440" end="2:02.510">ち</span><span begin="2:02.510" end="2:02.790">ゃ</span><span begin="2:02.790" end="2:02.950">い</span><span begin="2:03.070" end="2:03.390">け</span><span begin="2:03.390" end="2:03.970">な</span><span begin="2:03.970" end="2:05.170">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不能去相信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不能去相信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I shouldn&apos;t believe it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">믿어선 안 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne dois pas y croire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No debo creerlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich darf es nicht glauben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não devo acreditar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Нельзя верить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non devo crederci</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjicha ikenai</span></p><p begin="2:05.760" end="2:10.380" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:05.760" end="2:06.330">迷</span><span begin="2:06.330" end="2:07.280">信</span><span begin="2:07.280" end="2:07.460">ば</span><span begin="2:07.580" end="2:07.890">か</span><span begin="2:07.890" end="2:08.180">り</span><span begin="2:08.180" end="2:08.480">が</span><span begin="2:08.480" end="2:08.650">聞</span><span begin="2:08.760" end="2:09.400">こ</span><span begin="2:09.400" end="2:09.840">え</span><span begin="2:09.980" end="2:10.380">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">耳边听到的尽是迷信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">耳邊聽到的盡是迷信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I only hear superstitions</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">미신만이 들려와서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je n&apos;entends que des superstitions</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo escucho supersticiones</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich höre nur Aberglauben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Só ouço superstições</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Слышны лишь суеверия</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sento solo superstizioni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Meishin bakari ga kikoete</span></p><p begin="2:10.540" end="2:14.770" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.540" end="2:11.180">信</span><span begin="2:11.180" end="2:12.040">じ</span><span begin="2:12.040" end="2:12.110">ち</span><span begin="2:12.110" end="2:12.380">ゃ</span><span begin="2:12.380" end="2:12.560">い</span><span begin="2:12.670" end="2:12.980">け</span><span begin="2:12.980" end="2:13.590">な</span><span begin="2:13.590" end="2:14.770">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不能去相信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不能去相信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I shouldn&apos;t believe it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">믿어선 안 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne dois pas y croire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No debo creerlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich darf es nicht glauben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não devo acreditar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Нельзя верить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non devo crederci</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjicha ikenai</span></p><p begin="2:15.380" end="2:20.800" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:15.380" end="2:15.980">温</span><span begin="2:15.980" end="2:16.490">も</span><span begin="2:16.880" end="2:17.160">り</span><span begin="2:17.160" end="2:17.620">ば</span><span begin="2:17.750" end="2:18.090">か</span><span begin="2:18.090" end="2:18.330">り</span><span begin="2:18.330" end="2:18.520">欲</span><span begin="2:18.520" end="2:18.650">し</span><span begin="2:18.650" end="2:18.780">い</span><span begin="2:18.780" end="2:18.970">欲</span><span begin="2:18.970" end="2:19.110">し</span><span begin="2:19.110" end="2:19.240">い</span><span begin="2:19.240" end="2:19.520">欲</span><span begin="2:19.520" end="2:19.770">し</span><span begin="2:19.770" end="2:20.800">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唯独渴望渴望渴望那份温暖</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唯獨渴望渴望渴望那份溫暖</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I just want want want warmth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">온기만을 원해 원해 원해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne veux que de la chaleur j&apos;en veux j&apos;en veux j&apos;en veux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo quiero quiero quiero calidez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich sehne mich nur nach Wärme Wärme Wärme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Só quero quero quero o seu calor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лишь тепла хочу хочу хочу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio voglio voglio solo calore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nukumori bakari hoshii hoshii hoshii</span></p><p begin="2:21.310" end="2:25.770" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.310" end="2:21.840">爪</span><span begin="2:21.840" end="2:22.280">を</span><span begin="2:22.280" end="2:22.490">噛</span><span begin="2:22.590" end="2:22.870">む</span><span begin="2:22.870" end="2:23.050">た</span><span begin="2:23.050" end="2:23.460">び</span><span begin="2:23.460" end="2:23.620">に</span> <span begin="2:23.780" end="2:24.660">涙</span><span begin="2:24.660" end="2:24.850">散</span><span begin="2:24.850" end="2:25.260">る</span><span begin="2:25.260" end="2:25.450">散</span><span begin="2:25.450" end="2:25.770">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">每次咬指甲时 眼泪散落滴落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">每次咬指甲時 眼淚散落滴落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Every time I bite my nails tears scatter scatter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손톱을 물어뜯을 때마다 눈물이 지고 져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À chaque fois que je me ronge les ongles mes larmes tombent tombent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cada vez que me muerdo las uñas las lágrimas caen y caen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jedes Mal wenn ich Nägel kaue fallen fallen Tränen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda vez que roo as unhas as lágrimas caem caem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каждый раз кусая ногти слёзы падают падают</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ogni volta che mordo le unghie le lacrime cadono cadono</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsume o kamu tabi ni namida chiru chiru</span></p><p begin="2:26.120" end="2:30.380" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:26.120" end="2:26.780">切</span><span begin="2:26.780" end="2:27.220">な</span><span begin="2:27.640" end="2:27.960">さ</span><span begin="2:27.960" end="2:28.280">が</span><span begin="2:28.280" end="2:28.470">満</span><span begin="2:28.570" end="2:29.190">ち</span><span begin="2:29.190" end="2:30.380">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">悲痛满溢充盈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">悲痛滿溢充盈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Heartache fills up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애달픔이 차올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le chagrin déborde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La tristeza se desborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Schmerz erfüllt mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A angústia transborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тоска переполняет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La tristezza si colma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Setsunasa ga michiru</span></p><p begin="2:31.550" end="2:35.730" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:31.550" end="2:32.490">願</span><span begin="2:32.490" end="2:32.790">い</span><span begin="2:32.790" end="2:33.090">ど</span><span begin="2:33.090" end="2:33.410">お</span><span begin="2:33.410" end="2:33.660">り</span><span begin="2:33.660" end="2:33.910">に</span><span begin="2:34.010" end="2:34.580">な</span><span begin="2:34.580" end="2:34.780">ら</span><span begin="2:34.890" end="2:35.200">な</span><span begin="2:35.200" end="2:35.730">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">事与愿违</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">事與願違</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Things don&apos;t go as I wish</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">소원대로 되지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les choses ne se passent pas comme je le souhaite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las cosas no salen como deseo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es wird nicht wie ich es mir wünsche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As coisas não saem como eu desejo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё идёт не так как желаю</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non va come desidero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Negai doori ni naranai</span></p><p begin="2:36.640" end="2:40.350" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:36.640" end="2:36.950">夢</span><span begin="2:36.950" end="2:37.260">だ</span><span begin="2:37.260" end="2:37.540">け</span><span begin="2:37.540" end="2:37.860">見</span><span begin="2:37.860" end="2:38.170">て</span><span begin="2:38.170" end="2:38.470">い</span><span begin="2:38.470" end="2:38.750">る</span><span begin="2:38.750" end="2:39.650">ん</span><span begin="2:39.650" end="2:39.940">で</span><span begin="2:39.940" end="2:40.350">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只能沉浸在幻想的梦中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只能沉浸在幻想的夢中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I am only dreaming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꿈만 꾸고 있는 겁니다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne fais que rêver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo estoy soñando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich träume nur noch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estou apenas sonhando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я лишь вижу сны</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sto solo sognando</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yume dake mite irun desu</span></p><p begin="2:40.530" end="2:43.190" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:40.530" end="2:40.950">ま</span><span begin="2:40.950" end="2:41.020">っ</span><span begin="2:41.020" end="2:41.480">さ</span><span begin="2:41.480" end="2:41.670">ら</span><span begin="2:41.780" end="2:42.050">に</span><span begin="2:42.050" end="2:42.250">な</span><span begin="2:42.250" end="2:42.670">り</span><span begin="2:42.670" end="2:42.980">た</span><span begin="2:42.980" end="2:43.190">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想回到最初的纯白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想回到最初的純白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to become brand new</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">백지가 되고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux redevenir immaculée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero empezar de cero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte ganz rein werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero voltar a ser uma página em branco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хочу стать совершенно новой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio tornare immacolata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Massara ni naritai</span></p><p begin="2:43.250" end="2:49.700" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:43.250" end="2:43.860">傷</span><span begin="2:43.860" end="2:44.030">を</span><span begin="2:44.030" end="2:44.380">持</span><span begin="2:44.480" end="2:44.680">た</span><span begin="2:44.680" end="2:44.930">な</span><span begin="2:44.930" end="2:45.050">い</span> <span begin="2:45.360" end="2:45.690">あ</span><span begin="2:45.690" end="2:45.840">の</span><span begin="2:45.940" end="2:46.460">日</span><span begin="2:46.890" end="2:47.170">の</span><span begin="2:47.170" end="2:48.390">私</span><span begin="2:48.390" end="2:49.700">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">还不曾受过伤的 那天的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還不曾受過傷的 那天的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The me from that day without any scars</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">상처가 없던 그날의 나는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Celle que j&apos;étais ce jour-là et qui n&apos;avait aucune blessure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi yo de aquel día que no tenía heridas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein damaliges Ich das noch keine Wunden trug</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A mim daquele dia que não tinha feridas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Та я из того дня не имевшая ран</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La me di quel giorno che non aveva ferite</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kizu o motanai ano hi no watashi wa</span></p><p begin="2:50.170" end="2:53.670" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:50.170" end="2:50.750">黒</span><span begin="2:50.750" end="2:51.300">い</span><span begin="2:51.670" end="2:52.420">猫</span><span begin="2:52.570" end="2:53.170">か</span><span begin="2:53.170" end="2:53.670">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被那只黑猫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被那隻黑貓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">By a black cat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">검은 고양이에게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Par un chat noir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por un gato negro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Von der schwarzen Katze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por um gato preto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чёрной кошкой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da un gatto nero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuroi neko kara</span></p><p begin="2:54.040" end="2:59.750" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:54.040" end="2:54.550">引</span><span begin="2:54.550" end="2:54.660">っ</span><span begin="2:54.660" end="2:54.820">掻</span><span begin="2:54.950" end="2:55.270">か</span><span begin="2:55.270" end="2:55.440">れ</span><span begin="2:55.580" end="2:56.060">て</span><span begin="2:56.470" end="2:56.790">し</span><span begin="2:56.790" end="2:57.350">ま</span><span begin="2:57.600" end="2:58.020">っ</span><span begin="2:58.020" end="2:59.750">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">狠狠地抓伤了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">狠狠地抓傷了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I ended up getting scratched</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">할퀴어지고 말았어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;est fait griffer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Fui arañada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wurde ich zerkratzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acabei sendo arranhada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Была оцарапана</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È stata graffiata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hikkakarete shimatta</span></p><p begin="3:10.840" end="3:19.520" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:10.840" end="3:11.210">あ</span><span begin="3:11.210" end="3:11.930">な</span><span begin="3:12.070" end="3:12.410">た</span><span begin="3:12.410" end="3:12.850">は</span><span begin="3:13.310" end="3:14.790">私</span><span begin="3:14.790" end="3:15.290">を</span><span begin="3:15.690" end="3:16.360">愛</span><span begin="3:16.540" end="3:17.110">し</span><span begin="3:17.210" end="3:17.780">て</span><span begin="3:17.780" end="3:18.090">は</span><span begin="3:18.090" end="3:18.290">い</span><span begin="3:18.390" end="3:19.040">な</span><span begin="3:19.040" end="3:19.520">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你其实并不爱我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你其實並不愛我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You do not love me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신은 나를 사랑하지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu ne m&apos;aimes pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tú no me amas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du liebst mich nicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você não me ama</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты меня не любишь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tu non mi ami</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata wa watashi o aishite wa inai</span></p><p begin="3:20.160" end="3:24.610" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:20.160" end="3:20.670">満</span><span begin="3:20.670" end="3:21.380">月</span><span begin="3:21.380" end="3:21.600">の</span><span begin="3:21.600" end="3:22.260">下</span><span begin="3:22.260" end="3:22.540">で</span> <span begin="3:22.540" end="3:23.470">桜</span><span begin="3:23.470" end="3:23.650">散</span><span begin="3:23.650" end="3:24.080">る</span><span begin="3:24.080" end="3:24.290">散</span><span begin="3:24.290" end="3:24.610">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">满月之下 樱花飘落散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">滿月之下 櫻花飄落散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Under the full moon cherry blossoms scatter scatter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">만월 아래서 벚꽃이 지고 져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sous la pleine lune les fleurs de cerisier tombent tombent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Bajo la luna llena los cerezos caen y caen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unter dem Vollmond fallen fallen die Kirschblüten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sob a lua cheia as cerejeiras caem caem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Под полной луной сакура опадает опадает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sotto la luna piena i ciliegi cadono cadono</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mangetsu no shita de sakura chiru chiru</span></p><p begin="3:24.960" end="3:29.200" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:24.960" end="3:25.490">情</span><span begin="3:25.600" end="3:26.790">熱</span><span begin="3:26.790" end="3:27.110">は</span><span begin="3:27.110" end="3:27.280">満</span><span begin="3:27.380" end="3:28.010">ち</span><span begin="3:28.010" end="3:29.200">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">热情满溢充盈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">熱情滿溢充盈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Passion fills up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정열은 차올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La passion déborde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La pasión se desborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Leidenschaft erfüllt mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A paixão transborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Страсть переполняет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La passione si colma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jounetsu wa michiru</span></p><p begin="3:30.340" end="3:39.100" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.340" end="3:30.990">そ</span><span begin="3:30.990" end="3:31.320">の</span><span begin="3:31.320" end="3:31.850">優</span><span begin="3:31.850" end="3:32.030">し</span><span begin="3:32.130" end="3:32.470">さ</span><span begin="3:32.470" end="3:32.790">は</span><span begin="3:32.790" end="3:33.940">私</span><span begin="3:33.940" end="3:34.550">を</span><span begin="3:35.450" end="3:35.750">悲</span><span begin="3:35.750" end="3:35.940">し</span><span begin="3:36.050" end="3:36.310">く</span><span begin="3:36.310" end="3:36.620">さ</span><span begin="3:36.620" end="3:36.960">せ</span><span begin="3:36.960" end="3:37.240">る</span><span begin="3:37.240" end="3:37.570">だ</span><span begin="3:37.570" end="3:38.460">け</span><span begin="3:38.460" end="3:38.750">で</span><span begin="3:38.750" end="3:39.100">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那份温柔只会让我感到悲伤</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那份溫柔只會讓我感到悲傷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That kindness only makes me sad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 다정함은 나를 슬프게 할 뿐입니다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette gentillesse ne fait que m&apos;attrister</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa amabilidad solo me entristece</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diese Freundlichkeit macht mich nur traurig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Essa sua gentileza apenas me deixa triste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эта доброта лишь заставляет меня грустить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quella gentilezza mi rende solo triste</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono yasashisa wa watashi o kanashiku saseru dake desu</span></p><p begin="3:39.400" end="3:41.990" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:39.400" end="3:39.780">ま</span><span begin="3:39.780" end="3:39.850">っ</span><span begin="3:39.850" end="3:40.280">さ</span><span begin="3:40.280" end="3:40.590">ら</span><span begin="3:40.590" end="3:40.850">に</span><span begin="3:40.850" end="3:41.060">な</span><span begin="3:41.060" end="3:41.490">り</span><span begin="3:41.490" end="3:41.780">た</span><span begin="3:41.780" end="3:41.990">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想回到最初的纯白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想回到最初的純白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to become brand new</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">백지가 되고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux redevenir immaculée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero empezar de cero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte ganz rein werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero voltar a ser uma página em branco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хочу стать совершенно новой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio tornare immacolata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Massara ni naritai</span></p><p begin="3:42.060" end="3:48.500" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:42.060" end="3:42.300">あ</span><span begin="3:42.300" end="3:42.680">な</span><span begin="3:42.680" end="3:42.860">た</span><span begin="3:42.860" end="3:43.250">知</span><span begin="3:43.250" end="3:43.480">ら</span><span begin="3:43.480" end="3:43.680">な</span><span begin="3:43.680" end="3:43.830">い</span> <span begin="3:44.180" end="3:44.480">あ</span><span begin="3:44.480" end="3:44.730">の</span><span begin="3:44.730" end="3:45.250">日</span><span begin="3:45.690" end="3:45.980">の</span><span begin="3:45.980" end="3:47.200">私</span><span begin="3:47.200" end="3:48.500">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">还不认识你的 那天的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還不認識你的 那天的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The me from that day who didn&apos;t know you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신을 모르던 그날의 나는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Celle que j&apos;étais ce jour-là et que tu ne connais pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi yo de aquel día que no te conocía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein damaliges Ich das dich nicht kannte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A mim daquele dia que não te conhecia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Та я из того дня не знавшая тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La me di quel giorno che non ti conosceva</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata shiranai ano hi no watashi wa</span></p><p begin="3:48.910" end="3:58.840" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:48.910" end="3:49.580">月</span><span begin="3:49.580" end="3:50.100">の</span><span begin="3:50.450" end="3:51.970">光</span><span begin="3:51.970" end="3:52.460">に</span><span begin="3:52.890" end="3:53.450">瞞</span><span begin="3:53.450" end="3:53.610">か</span><span begin="3:53.710" end="3:54.050">さ</span><span begin="3:54.050" end="3:54.240">れ</span><span begin="3:54.370" end="3:54.890">て</span><span begin="3:55.260" end="3:55.600">し</span><span begin="3:55.600" end="3:56.150">ま</span><span begin="3:56.420" end="3:56.790">っ</span><span begin="3:56.790" end="3:58.840">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被那月光彻底蒙蔽了双眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被那月光徹底蒙蔽了雙眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Was completely deceived by the moonlight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">달빛에 속아 넘어가 버렸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">A été trompée par la lumière de la lune</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Fui engañada por la luz de la luna</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wurde vom Mondlicht getäuscht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fui enganada pela luz da lua</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Была обманута лунным светом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È stata ingannata dalla luce della luna</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuki no hikari ni mayakasarete shimatta</span></p><p begin="4:00.030" end="4:03.950" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:00.030" end="4:00.790">昨日</span><span begin="4:01.270" end="4:01.570">あ</span><span begin="4:01.570" end="4:02.010">な</span><span begin="4:02.500" end="4:02.790">た</span><span begin="4:02.790" end="4:03.300">は</span><span begin="4:03.300" end="4:03.460">言</span><span begin="4:03.460" end="4:03.540">っ</span><span begin="4:03.540" end="4:03.710">て</span><span begin="4:03.710" end="4:03.950">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">昨天你曾对我说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">昨天你曾對我說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Yesterday you said</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어제 당신은 말했지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Hier tu as dit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ayer tú dijiste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gestern hast du gesagt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ontem você disse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вчера ты сказал</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ieri tu hai detto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kinou anata wa itteta</span></p><p begin="4:04.250" end="4:08.690" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:04.250" end="4:04.280">「</span><span begin="4:04.280" end="4:04.600">永</span><span begin="4:04.600" end="4:04.870">遠</span><span begin="4:04.870" end="4:04.980">を</span><span begin="4:05.090" end="4:05.320">誓</span><span begin="4:05.320" end="4:05.460">っ</span><span begin="4:05.460" end="4:05.630">た</span><span begin="4:05.630" end="4:05.930">人</span><span begin="4:05.930" end="4:06.070">が</span><span begin="4:06.070" end="4:06.230">い</span><span begin="4:06.230" end="4:06.380">る</span><span begin="4:06.380" end="4:06.520">ん</span><span begin="4:06.520" end="4:06.600">だ</span><span begin="4:06.600" end="4:06.670">、</span><span begin="4:06.670" end="4:06.820">だ</span><span begin="4:06.820" end="4:06.980">か</span><span begin="4:06.980" end="4:07.290">ら</span><span begin="4:07.290" end="4:07.320">、</span><span begin="4:07.910" end="4:08.240">ご</span><span begin="4:08.240" end="4:08.550">め</span><span begin="4:08.550" end="4:08.660">ん</span><span begin="4:08.660" end="4:08.690">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">「我已经有互誓永远的人了，所以，对不起」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「我已經有互誓永遠的人了，所以，對不起」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">&quot;There is someone I swore eternity to, so, I&apos;m sorry&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「영원을 맹세한 사람이 있어, 그러니까, 미안해」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">« Il y a quelqu&apos;un à qui j&apos;ai juré l&apos;éternité, alors, désolé »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">«Hay alguien a quien le juré eternidad, por eso, lo siento»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">„Es gibt jemanden dem ich die Ewigkeit geschworen habe, also, tut mir leid“</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">«Há alguém a quem jurei eternidade, por isso, me desculpe»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">«Есть человек которому я поклялся в вечности, поэтому, прости»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">«C&apos;è una persona a cui ho giurato eternità, perciò, scusami»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Eien o chikatta hito ga irunda, dakara, gomen&quot;</span></p></div></body></tt>